{"title":"Java JDK下载安装及环境配置超详细图文教程","uid":"6d85ccd1149a1b677fbaa270c9512e58","slug":"Java JDK下载安装及环境配置超详细图文教程","date":"2021-03-15T10:51:22.000Z","updated":"2022-03-14T14:23:21.268Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Java JDK下载安装及环境配置超详细图文教程.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://cover.png","content":"<h1 id=\"Java-JDK下载安装及环境配置超详细图文教程\"><a href=\"#Java-JDK下载安装及环境配置超详细图文教程\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Java JDK下载安装及环境配置超详细图文教程\"></a>Java JDK下载安装及环境配置超详细图文教程</h1><h2 id=\"1-JDK下载（点击可跳过下面步骤直接进入下载界面）\"><a href=\"#1-JDK下载（点击可跳过下面步骤直接进入下载界面）\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1. JDK下载（点击可跳过下面步骤直接进入下载界面）\"></a>1. <a href=\"https://www.oracle.com/java/technologies/javase-downloads.html\">JDK下载</a>（点击可跳过下面步骤直接进入下载界面）</h2><p>1.1 打开浏览器输入网址 <a href=\"https://www.oracle.com/index.html\">https://www.oracle.com/index.html</a>，进入<a href=\"https://www.oracle.com/index.html\">Oracle官网</a><br><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210315170447356.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L0FDRV9VXzAwNUE=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\"><br>1.2 在官网首页菜单栏，点击Products，在Software中找到Java，单击该选项<br><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210315171406120.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L0FDRV9VXzAwNUE=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\"><br>会进入如下界面<br><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/2021031517353215.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L0FDRV9VXzAwNUE=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\"></p>\n<p>1.3 在界面中往下滑，可以看到如下选项，在该选项中选择Java SE，找到Oracle JDK，点击进入JDK下载界面<br><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210315171841969.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L0FDRV9VXzAwNUE=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\"><br><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210315173812890.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L0FDRV9VXzAwNUE=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\"><br>1.4 在该界面可以找到各种版本的JDK，选择自己需要的版本进行下载即可。在这里本人选择JDK1.8版本进行示范下载安装<br><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210315174141900.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L0FDRV9VXzAwNUE=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\"><br>1.5 进入后选择电脑对应的64位版本，假如不确定电脑类型，可按win+r打开运行，输入msinfo32，回车确定后即可查看电脑配置信息<br><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210315175136138.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L0FDRV9VXzAwNUE=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\"><br>1.6 确定好之后选择对应的exe文件格式，点击进行下载<br><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210315174313571.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L0FDRV9VXzAwNUE=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\"><br>点击后会弹出一个通知，同意接受，点击安装，未登录的用户可能会弹出登录界面，假如没有Oracle账号创建账号进行登录后即可下载安装<br><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210315174431737.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L0FDRV9VXzAwNUE=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"2-JDK安装\"><a href=\"#2-JDK安装\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2. JDK安装\"></a>2. JDK安装</h2><p>2.1 下载完JDK到本地后，找到该文件，双击运行JDK安装程序（这里我使用的是以前下载的JDK，按上述方式下载同样会得到这样一个文件）</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210316181258234.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L0FDRV9VXzAwNUE=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\"></p>\n<p>2.2 等待一会，进入JDK安装界面，点击下一步<br><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/202103151810353.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L0FDRV9VXzAwNUE=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\"></p>\n<p>2.3 可以直接默认目录，点击下一步。也可以自行选择创建一个新的空文件夹，建议在C盘（有些工具需要JDK装在C盘），先创建一个文件夹名为Java，再在该文件夹下创建一个文件夹为JDK安装目录，同时创建一个文件夹为JRE安装目录<br><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210315181058529.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L0FDRV9VXzAwNUE=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\"><br><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210315181335948.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L0FDRV9VXzAwNUE=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\"><br>2.4 然后回到JDK安装界面，更改安装路径，为上述所创建的JDK路径，点击下一步（这里由于第一项开发工具中已经自带了 JRE，则第三项的公共 JRE 可以取消独立安装，上述创建的 JRE 文件夹也不需要了）<br><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210315181321681.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L0FDRV9VXzAwNUE=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\"><br>2.5 等待一会，会进入 JRE 的安装界面，同样的更改路径，为上述所创建的 JRE 路径，更改完之后点击下一步（在上一步取消公共 JRE 安装的则不会出现下面的界面，直接到 2.6 安装完成）<br><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210315181725356.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L0FDRV9VXzAwNUE=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\"><br><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210315181828780.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L0FDRV9VXzAwNUE=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\"><br>2.6 至此JDK已经安装完毕，点击关闭<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210315182239510.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L0FDRV9VXzAwNUE=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\"><br>2.7 若想验证是否安装成功，可按win+r，输入cmd进入命令提示符（可参照前面的查看电脑配置信息操作），在命令提示符界面输入java，出现如下界面即表示安装成功（未选择上面公共 JRE 独立安装的则不会有下面的显示，而为<br>’java‘ 不是内部或外部命令，也不是可运行的程序或批处理文件<br> 需配置环境变量即可有下面的界面）<br><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210315182209316.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L0FDRV9VXzAwNUE=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"3-环境配置\"><a href=\"#3-环境配置\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"3. 环境配置\"></a>3. 环境配置</h2><p>3.1 右键单击此电脑，点击属性，会出现以下设置选项，点击高级系统设置，打开<br><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/202103151833283.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L0FDRV9VXzAwNUE=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\"><br>3.2 点击环境变量<br><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/202103151834274.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L0FDRV9VXzAwNUE=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\"><br>3.3 点击新建，变量名为JAVA_HOME,变量值为刚刚JDK安装的路径，点击确定<br><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210315183601917.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L0FDRV9VXzAwNUE=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\"><br>3.4 双击path，进入界面后，点击编辑文本<br><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210315184042998.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L0FDRV9VXzAwNUE=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\"><br><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210315184117381.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L0FDRV9VXzAwNUE=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\"></p>\n<p>3.5 在变量值的最开头输入<br>%JAVA_HOME%\\bin;%JAVA_HOME%\\jre\\bin;<br>不要对其他数值进行修改（由于我已经进行了配置，所以显示在了中间，第一次输入在最开头即可），假如不小心修改了其他数值，取消重新进入即可。（在前面取消安装了公共 JRE 的则只需要在变量值的最开头输入：<br>%JAVA_HOME%\\bin;<br>即可）<br><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210315184352152.png\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\"><br>3.6 点击确定，全部确定退出后，依旧按win+r，输入cmd进入命令提示符界面，输入javac，假如出现如下界面则配置成功。（这时再输入 java，则会出现 2.7 所示界面）<br><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210315184552196.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L0FDRV9VXzAwNUE=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\"><br><strong>结尾：至此，Java JDK下载安装及环境配置已完全成功</strong></p>\n","feature":false,"text":"Java JDK下载安装及环境配置超详细图文教程1. JDK下载（点击可跳过下面步骤直接进入下载界面）1.1 打开浏览器输入网址 https://www.oracle.com/index.html，进入Oracle官网1.2 在官网首页菜单栏，点击Products，在Softwa...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"1.5k","symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"开发工具环境","slug":"开发工具环境","count":6,"path":"api/categories/开发工具环境.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Java","slug":"Java","count":6,"path":"api/tags/Java.json"},{"name":"IDEA","slug":"IDEA","count":4,"path":"api/tags/IDEA.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Java-JDK%E4%B8%8B%E8%BD%BD%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E5%8F%8A%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E8%B6%85%E8%AF%A6%E7%BB%86%E5%9B%BE%E6%96%87%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Java JDK下载安装及环境配置超详细图文教程</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#1-JDK%E4%B8%8B%E8%BD%BD%EF%BC%88%E7%82%B9%E5%87%BB%E5%8F%AF%E8%B7%B3%E8%BF%87%E4%B8%8B%E9%9D%A2%E6%AD%A5%E9%AA%A4%E7%9B%B4%E6%8E%A5%E8%BF%9B%E5%85%A5%E4%B8%8B%E8%BD%BD%E7%95%8C%E9%9D%A2%EF%BC%89\"><span class=\"toc-text\">1. JDK下载（点击可跳过下面步骤直接进入下载界面）</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#2-JDK%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85\"><span class=\"toc-text\">2. JDK安装</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#3-%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE\"><span class=\"toc-text\">3. 环境配置</span></a></li></ol></li></ol>","author":{"name":"凡","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210313122054101.png","link":"/","description":"","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/Fan223","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"https://weibo.com/u/7318914058","zhihu":"https://www.zhihu.com/people/tridiamond","csdn":"https://blog.csdn.net/ACE_U_005A","juejin":"https://juejin.cn/user/1873223546578589","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"prev_post":{"title":"IntelliJ IDEA 下载安装及配置超详细图文教程","uid":"eff30bb7d086b3412ad27d9c98560636","slug":"IntelliJ IDEA 下载安装及配置超详细图文教程","date":"2021-03-18T10:20:48.000Z","updated":"2022-03-14T14:23:15.665Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/IntelliJ IDEA 下载安装及配置超详细图文教程.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://cover.png","text":"IntelliJ IDEA 下载安装及配置超详细图文教程1. Idea 下载（可跳过下面步骤点击直接进入下载界面）1.1 打开浏览器输入https://www.jetbrains.com/，进入jetbrains官网，在Developer Tools中找到 Intellij ID...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"1.2k","symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"开发工具环境","slug":"开发工具环境","count":6,"path":"api/categories/开发工具环境.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Java","slug":"Java","count":6,"path":"api/tags/Java.json"},{"name":"IDEA","slug":"IDEA","count":4,"path":"api/tags/IDEA.json"}],"author":{"name":"凡","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210313122054101.png","link":"/","description":"","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/Fan223","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"https://weibo.com/u/7318914058","zhihu":"https://www.zhihu.com/people/tridiamond","csdn":"https://blog.csdn.net/ACE_U_005A","juejin":"https://juejin.cn/user/1873223546578589","customs":{}}},"feature":false},"next_post":{}}